(15, 3, '2009-02-02 15:57:00', 'Magento version 1.2.1 is now available for download and upgrade', 'We are happy to announce the availability of Magento version 1.2.1 for download and upgrade.\n\nThis version includes some issue resolutions for Magento version 1.2.x. A full list of items included in this release can be found on the release notes page.', 'http://www.magentocommerce.com/blog/comments/magento-version-121-now-available/', 1, 0),
